name: Crypto Monster "BABY MAGGOT" in Nano Fractal
description: I create world of digital monsters from parts of female body. Each body is unique and beautiful, incomparable with others, and cannot be generalized. I use digital glazing to enhance uniqueness through different color correlations and eye focus points. The art of observing one object multiplies and reveals its various essences and sides. Each of my monsters has passed a long evolutionary way from a single-celled formless creature to who they are...
